(Trigger): PlayerJoined

IfThenElse
  If
    $playerRole
    =
    Guest
Then
+ Commands

/role $player {role you want to role them; must be spelled exactly the same. CaPs SeNsItIvE}


Example:

PlayerJoined

IfThenElse
  If
    $playerRole
    =
    Guest
 Then
 + Commands
 
